targets.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("result_dht_bytes_out"), 1m) FROM "http_process_info_v1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "host" fill(null)
SELECT (100 - ( last("result_diskfree") / last("result_disktotal") ) * 100 ) FROM "http_space_local_v1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "host" fill(none)
SELECT (last("result_used")  / last("result_donated")) * 100 FROM "http_space_donated_v1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "host" fill(none)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("result_node-connected"), 20s) FROM "http_event_list_v1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(20s), "host" fill(null)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("result_node-disconnected"), 20s) FROM "http_event_list_v1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(20s), "host" fill(null)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("result_identity-rotated"), 20s) FROM "http_event_list_v1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(20s), "host" fill(null)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("result_my-identity-rotated"), 20s) FROM "http_event_list_v1" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(20s), "host" fill(null)
